name: politico
text: President Trump’s campaign is reorienting its summer TV ad strategy to focus on states that will begin voting sooner than others, after the reelection went dark on TV in an unusual move this week, leaving the airwaves to Joe Biden https://t.co/7ki11FPt7S

name: politico
text: Trump advisers declined to specify which states the ads would be focused on, but there are several key battlegrounds at the front of the early voting calendar https://t.co/7ki11FPt7S
